      <h1 class="hero h1">The AI Coding Agent</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Built for GDPR‑grade privacy. InnoCode ships with InnoGPT — EU‑hosted models and one API key for everything.</p>

      <div class="install-box">
        <div class="install-tabs">
